## A Note on Sources

### Reporting Methodology

- Based on **hundreds of interviews** and **thousands of papers and studies**
- Sources detailed in text, notes, with guides to additional resources
- Major sources given opportunity to **review facts** after reporting complete, offer comments, address discrepancies
- Comments reproduced in notes (no source given access to complete text — comments based on summaries)

### Confidentiality and Privacy

- Very small number of cases: confidentiality extended to sources who couldn't speak on-attribution basis
- Very tiny number: identifying characteristics **withheld or modified** to conform with patient privacy laws

