divorce, new home) alter buying patterns, though specific correlations
between life events and products remain difficult to pin down. General
trend holds per research by Alan Andreasen and others.
- **And they care quite a bit** — Extensive research on how particular
moments offer opportunities for marketers, government agencies, health
