- **"Why did I do it?"** — Stuart Jeffries article on sleep disorder
when lights go out (The Guardian, December 2009).
- **"His mind had no control"** — Richard Smith on grandad killed wife
during dream (The Mirror, November 2009).
- **"A straight not guilty verdict"** — Anthony Stone on nightmare man
